Blood, Toil, Sweat & Tears!
The making of the MakeMeUp Festival has been a
journey!
All the effort, the late nights, the happy highs &
emotional lows have all been worth it!
Watch the Behind the scenes of our Fashion show,
that was put together by our Senior faculty &
students at the MakeMeUp School of Makeup!
It was definitely a moment of pride to watch our
students put in so much effort & shine bright on the
stage!
Kudos, to the entire team!
This is just the beginning, let's relive the MakeMeUp
Festival '22 virtually, and for those who missed it,
this is just a glimpse, more videos to follow!
